{"id": "1339513522387812413", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 0, "author_id": "329639869855039498", "author_name": "dekopon4682", "author_bot": false, "content": "ありがとうございます\nドールも強いんですねー、＋４が全てのダメージのバフなのは確かに強そう\n一旦、深海のキャラ集めてみます！", "timestamp": "2025-02-13T08:28:30.695000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
